longBusinessSummary: Habersham Bancorp does not have significant operations. Previously, the company, operated as the bank holding company for Habersham Bank that provided commercial banking services to businesses and individuals in Habersham, White, Cherokee, Warren, Stephens, Forsyth, and Hall Counties in Georgia. Habersham Bancorp was founded in 1904 and is based in Cornelia, Georgia.
